"title": "4971: seasons, of life",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4971",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Appropriate or appointed periods of time which are part of the variety and development of human life and experience and which influence human affairs. The times and seasons for individuals and nations are set by God, who works all things together towards the final fulfilment of his purposes.</p>\n<h2>The seasons of life are appointed by God</h2>\n<h3>The seasons of individual lives</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:1-Eccl3:8\">ECC 3:1–3:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:15\">PSA 31:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job14:5\">JOB 14:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:16\">PSA 139:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:11\">ECC 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:28\">ROM 8:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:13-Jas4:15\">JAS 4:13–4:15</a></p>\n<h3>The seasons of nations and the world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:21\">DAN 2:21</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:26\">ACT 17:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:17\">DAN 4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:25\">DAN 7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:7\">ACT 1:7</a></p>\n<h2>A time to die</h2>\n<h3>The transience of human life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:15-Ps103:16\">PSA 103:15–103:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:6-Job7:8\">JOB 7:6–7:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job14:1-Job14:2\">JOB 14:1–14:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:2\">PSA 37:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:11\">PSA 102:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl6:12\">ECC 6:12</a></p>\n<h3>Death comes at its appointed time</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:26\">JOB 5:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen47:29\">GEN 47:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:1\">1KI 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:20\">LUK 12:20</a></p>\n<h2>Times of sadness and joy</h2>\n<h3>A time to mourn</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:41\">GEN 27:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:34\">GEN 37:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:3-Gen50:4\">GEN 50:3–50:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut34:8\">DEU 34:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:28\">JER 4:28</a></p>\n<h3>A time to rejoice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:21-John16:22\">JHN 16:21–16:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:47\">DEU 28:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth9:22\">EST 9:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:2-Isa61:3\">ISA 61:2–61:3</a></p>\n<h2>A time to speak</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:23\">PRO 15:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:11\">PRO 25:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:2\">2TI 4:2</a> <em>Christians are to be always ready to share the gospel.</em></p>\n<h2>Times appointed for the world</h2>\n<h3>The rise and fall of nations</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:37-Dan2:45\">DAN 2:37–2:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:19-Dan8:25\">DAN 8:19–8:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:2-Dan11:4\">DAN 11:2–11:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:24-Dan11:27\">DAN 11:24–11:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:24\">LUK 21:24</a></p>\n<h3>The time to receive God's salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:2\">2CO 6:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:8\">ISA 49:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:6\">ISA 55:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:7\">HEB 4:7</a></p>\n<h3>The time of God's judgment</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:35\">DEU 32:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek30:3\">EZK 30:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph2:2\">ZEP 2:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:31\">ACT 17:31</a></p>\n<h2>Times appointed for God's people</h2>\n<h3>Times for worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:4\">LEV 23:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:18\">EXO 34:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num9:2-Num9:3\">NUM 9:2–9:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num10:10\">NUM 10:10</a></p>\n<h3>Times of blessing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:13\">PSA 102:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:26\">EZK 34:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:19\">ACT 3:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:17\">ACT 7:17</a></p>\n<h3>A time of vindication</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:21-Dan7:22\">DAN 7:21–7:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:6\">ACT 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:18\">ROM 8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:6\">1PE 5:6</a></p>\n<h3>Times of testing</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:10\">PSA 66:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:3\">EZK 21:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:21\">MAT 13:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark4:17\">MRK 4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:13\">LUK 8:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:6-1Pet1:7\">1PE 1:6–1:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">REV 2:10</a></p>\n<h3>Times for withdrawal or solitude</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:35\">MRK 1:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:2-1Kgs17:6\">1KI 17:2–17:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:30-Mark6:32\">MRK 6:30–6:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:17\">GAL 1:17</a></p>\n<h3>Waiting for God's appointed time</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:3\">HAB 2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:23-Rom8:25\">ROM 8:23–8:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:28\">HEB 9:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:13\">HEB 11:13</a></p>\n<h2>Times appointed for Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>The appointed time of his birth</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:4\">GAL 4:4</a></p>\n<h3>The appointed time of his death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:23\">JHN 12:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:18\">MAT 26:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:41\">MRK 14:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:51\">LUK 9:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John2:4\">JHN 2:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:6-John7:8\">JHN 7:6–7:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:27\">JHN 12:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:1\">JHN 13:1</a></p>\n<h3>The appointed time of his return</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:8\">LUK 21:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:20-Acts3:21\">ACT 3:20–3:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:31\">ACT 17:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:5\">1CO 4:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:3\">REV 1:3</a></p>",
